# /apg-requirement-clarify

## Purpose

Clarify vague feature or change requests before implementation.

## Steps

1. Restate the requested outcome.
2. Identify affected flows, contracts, and dangerous modules.
3. Ask targeted questions about compatibility, tests, and review needs.
4. Produce a short requirement summary before any implementation plan.

## Stop conditions

Do not code while acceptance criteria, affected contracts, or migration/legacy behavior are unclear.
